which is our highest law.

00:10:35.460 --> 00:10:42.300 position:56%
And if any law passed by Congress is
in conflict with the Constitution,

00:10:42.300 --> 00:10:45.700
the Constitution prevails.

00:10:45.700 --> 00:10:52.000
So, our job is to say
what the national law is.

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:56.970
Sometimes, Congress writes
