disagree about what they mean.

00:11:02.350 --> 00:11:07.430
So we interpret statutes,
laws passed by Congress,

00:11:07.430 --> 00:11:14.150
and our highest law,
the U.S. Constitution.

00:11:15.920 --> 00:11:19.460
&gt;&gt; DEBBIE LEVY: And there
