we'll sit for two weeks.

00:11:52.190 --> 00:11:57.210
And on Wednesday, we'll all meet
together to talk about cases

00:11:57.210 --> 00:11:58.510
that were argued on Monday.

00:11:58.510 --> 00:12:01.890
And then we meet on Friday to talk

00:12:01.890 --> 00:12:04.760
about the Tuesday and
Wednesday cases.

00:12:04.760 --> 00:12:08.580
We go around the table; the
Chief Justice speaks first,

00:12:08.580 --> 00:12:12.570
but he has only one vote
