because they got divorced.

00:50:30.450 --> 00:50:35.580
And the mother took care of the
child when he was very young,

00:50:35.580 --> 00:50:40.360 position:56%
but when the boy was a teenager, his
father said, "Family Court judge,

00:50:40.360 --> 00:50:43.180
give the boy to me because
he has to be prepared

00:50:43.180 --> 00:50:45.250
to live in a man's world."

00:50:45.250 --> 00:50:49.090
His mother did not want the
father to have the child,

00:50:49.090 --> 00:50:52.180
but the judge ruled in
favor of the father.

00:50:52.180 --> 00:50:59.810 position:56%
The mother, sadly, was right because
the boy became very sad, depressed.

00:50:59.810 --> 00:51:01.120
And one day, he took out one

00:51:01.120 --> 00:51:05.690
